title: Real Life
lyrics:
Paroles de la chanson Real Life par Kimbra
If I had to find a process
What it would it be?
To try to make progress
Where would I reach?

? for regret to invade
In my real life, real life, real
Now it's real life, real life, real

I had to find my progress
My heart to be unbroken
Would I change real life, real life, real
Was real life, real life, real?
It's real life, real life, real
Real life, real life, real


There's nothing to find, nothing to find
The time to be alive
Trying to make sense of it
There's nothing to find, nothing to find
Nothing to be if you lose your mind
Try to make sense of it

There's nothing to find, nothing to find
Nobody got time in the real life
